Building Continuum

 These build instructions assumes you're building Continuum on a unix.

*Check out the sources

+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
$ export CVSROOT=:pserver:anoncvs@cvs.continuum.codehaus.org:/scm/continuum
$ cvs co continuum-new
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

*Build it

+--------------+
$ cd continuum
$ make.sh
+--------------+

 The make scrip will make a Continuum runtime in
<<<continuum-web/generated-runtime>>>

*Run it

+--------------------------------+
$ cd continuum-web
$ generated-runtime/bin/plexus.sh
+--------------------------------+
